# File Safety Guide

## Critical runtime files (edit carefully)

| File | Risk | Notes |
|------|------|-------|
| `script.js` | High | All app logic — test navigation, predictions, XP, polling after any change |
| `server.mjs` | High | Backend + API proxy — test live polling and match resolution |
| `index.html` | Medium | App shell — verify all views render, wallet sheet works |
| `styles.css` | Medium | All styles — check mobile layout after visual changes |
| `i18n.js` | Medium | Must keep EN and RU in sync — add keys to both locales |
| `identity.js` | Low | Simple identity state — used by wallet bundle |

## Config files (safe to edit)

| File | Notes |
|------|-------|
| `tracked-matches.json` | Match API config — update when changing tracked matches |
| `package.json` | Dependencies and scripts |
| `.env.example` | Placeholder env template |

## Generated files (do not edit by hand)

| File | Notes |
|------|-------|
| `wallet.bundle.js` | Built from `web3/` — rebuild with `npm run build:wallet` |
| `package-lock.json` | Auto-generated by npm |
